{{!-- Grid-row Mixin Begin --}}

  <h6>Grid-row mixin</h6>
  <div class="code-container">

  {{#markdown}}
  ```scss
  @mixin grid-row($behavior: false);

  ```
  {{/markdown}}
  </div>

  <ul class="disc">
    <li>The Grid-row mixin is used for creating container, nested, and collapsed rows. The behavior options include the following:</li>
  </ul>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="large-7 columns">
      <div class="code-container">
{{#markdown}}
```scss
.custom-class-name {
  @include grid-row();
}
```
{{/markdown}}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="large-5 columns"><p><kbd>Container</kbd> to use a container row. This option is set to the default.</p></div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="large-7 columns">
      <div class="code-container">
{{#markdown}}
```scss
.custom-class-name2 {
  @include grid-row(nest);
}
```
{{/markdown}}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="large-5 columns">
      <p><kbd>nest</kbd> to include a nested row</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="large-7 columns">
      <div class="code-container">
{{#markdown}}
```scss
.custom-class-name3 {
  @include grid-row(collapse);
}
```
{{/markdown}}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="large-5 columns">
      <p><kbd>collapse</kbd> to include a grid where container row margins collapse</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="large-7 columns">
      <div class="code-container">
{{#markdown}}
```scss
.custom-class-name4 {
  @include grid-row(nest-collapse);
}
```
{{/markdown}}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="large-5 columns">
      <p><kbd>nest-collapse</kbd> to include a grid where outer margins on a nested row collapse</p>
    </div>
  </div>

{{!-- Grid-row Mixin End --}}

{{!-- Grid-column Mixin Begin --}}

  <h6>Grid-Column mixin</h6>

  <ul class="disc">
    <li>The grid-column mixin is used for inside of media queries for controlling layouts.</li>
  </ul>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="large-7 columns">
      <div class="code-container">
{{#markdown}}
```scss
@mixin grid-column(
  $columns:false,
  $last-column:false,
  $center:false,
  $offset:false,
  $push:false,
  $pull:false,
  $collapse:false,
  $float:true
);
```
{{/markdown}}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="large-5 columns">
      <p>These are all of the options available for you to use with the grid-column mixin. Please see specific examples below for further customization of the mixin.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="large-7 columns">
      <div class="code-container">
{{#markdown}}
```scss
.custom-class-1 {
  @include grid-column(8);
}
```
{{/markdown}}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="large-5 columns">
      <p>The <kbd>columns</kbd> option is set explicitly with a numeric value depending on how many columns you wish your element to use.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="large-7 columns">
{{#markdown}}
```scss
.custom-class-2{
  @include grid-row(8, true);
}
```
{{/markdown}}
    </div>
    <div class="large-5 columns">
      <p>The <kbd>last-column</kbd> option checks wether this is the last column, and if it returns true, the last column will be floated in the opposite direction.</p>
    </div>
  </div>



{{!-- Grid-column Mixin End --}}

